  </div>

  <div class="static-page-content">
    <section>
      <h2>Return Eligibility</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>30-day return window from delivery date</li>
        <li>Items must be unworn, unwashed, and with original tags</li>
        <li>Original packaging must be included</li>
        <li>Receipt or proof of purchase required</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Return Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Login to your account or contact customer service</li>
        <li>Generate a return label</li>
        <li>Pack items securely with all original tags</li>
        <li>Ship using provided return label</li>
        <li>Allow 5-7 business days for processing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Sale items marked as final sale</li>
        <li>Intimates and swimwear</li>
        <li>Items damaged through customer use</li>
        <li>Items without original tags</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
